    "asOf": "2026-01-27",
    "date": "2026-06-04T14:36:44Z",
    "text": "Combating Online Predators Act or the COP Act\n\nThis bill establishes new federal criminal offenses for threatening to distribute a visual depiction of a minor (or person believed to be a minor) engaging in sexually explicit conduct with the intent that the minor (or person believed to be a minor) create or transmit a visual depiction of sexually explicit conduct. (This practice is commonly referred to as sextortion.)\u00a0The bill also prohibits attempts and conspiracies to commit the offenses.\u00a0"
  },
